name: GeekSoft
tag_list: file-expert, mobile-developer, android-app, ios-developer, android-developer, mobile-internet, ishare
overview:
GeekSoft is a fast-growing company which focuses on providing the file management and sharing solutions of both Android and iOS smart phone platform.

At present, GeekSoft has launched two main products: one is the famous free file manager File Expert, the other one is the file sharing app iShare.

File Expert enjoys a great popularity around the world. Till Dec 31, 2012, there are more than 18 millions smart phone users using File Expert to manage their mobile phone or tablet files every day.

In 2011, GeekSoft was honored as one of the TOP 30 Mobile Internet Application Development Cutting-Edge Companies in China.

In 2012, GeekSoft was honored as One of Three Most Influential International App Service Providers in Shaanxi Internet Conference in China.
